# Product List Filter

A dynamic product list filtering application built using **HTML**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Vanilla JavaScript**.  
This project demonstrates real-time filtering of products by category using JavaScript array methods and DOM manipulation without any JavaScript frameworks.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Dynamic rendering of product cards from JavaScript data
- Category-based filtering (e.g., All, Electronics, Clothing, etc.)
- Instant UI updates without page reload
- Event-driven interaction using JavaScript
- Clean and responsive layout using Tailwind CSS

